If you are an adult they will advertise to you, and I have no doubt that there are plenty of advertisers who will make adult only ads.  You tube really doesn’t want to lose the ad money they get from children.  That is the real problem.  Will them not tracking a child’s data, or not showing them personalized ads  affect the creators?  Absolutely.  Will it also affect you tube? Enormously!  That is the reason You tube is trying to put the responsibility on the creators.
